reviewText: Are all parts in english?

Mostly fillers, but fairy tails fillers are fillers I could deal with. Mainly because there so good. At times you would never even notice your watching filler. Please don't avoid this great anime due to fillers. I'm sure you'll still love it. Before anybody says anything, I know its not out yet, but I'm one of the anime lovers who already watched this season subbed. So I'm ahead of you story wise if you waited on the dvd release, sorry. :P

Love this anime so much and have spent the last couple of months collecting the dvds and this is no different.
My only problem I have with this dvd part was when i got it the box was pretty much destoryed there are chucks missing from the bottom and the opening side for the dvd box. When I opened it up so of the discs had fallen out of their holdings. and the push to release the dvds are missing the little parts that holds the dvds in place. Im a little afraid that the discs are going to fall out.

If anyone knows if its possible to buy a plastic dvd box with the 2 dvd pages that are in the box. If i could i would just buy the dvd box if I could.
